## 複製為 .env 後依環境修改（勿將含真實密碼的 .env 提交版本庫）
## docker compose 會讀取 .env；變數可在 shell 或 CI 覆寫

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MinIO / S3（必填：ACCESS / SECRET；其餘可選）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=your_access_key
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=your_secret_key

# 本機直跑 Flask：host:port 或 http://host:port（見 config.py 預設）
MINIO_ENDPOINT=127.0.0.1:9000
MINIO_ENDPOINT_CLIENT=127.0.0.1:9000

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# docker-compose.yml（僅起 web，連「外部」MinIO）
# 請改為容器內可連到的位址，例如區網或 host.docker.internal
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://192.168.1.100:9000
# MINIO_ENDPOINT_CLIENT=192.168.1.100:9000
# 若 MinIO 跑在宿主機、埠 9000（Windows / Mac Docker Desktop）可嘗試：
# MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://host.docker.internal:9000
# MINIO_ENDPOINT_CLIENT=host.docker.internal:9000

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# docker-compose(new_minio).yml / docker-compose - ubuntu.yml
# （同一份 compose 內含 MinIO 服務名 minio 時請用）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MINIO_ENDPOINT=http://minio:9000
# MINIO_ENDPOINT_CLIENT=minio:9000
# MINIO_ROOT_USER=minioadmin
# MINIO_ROOT_PASSWORD=minioadmin

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# S3A / Spark
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
S3A_PATH_STYLE_ACCESS=true
S3A_IMPL=org.apache.hadoop.fs.s3a.S3AFileSystem
S3A_ENDPOINT_REGION=us-east-1
S3A_CONNECTION_SSL_ENABLED=false

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Delta Lake 路徑（若改 BUCKET_NAME，請一併調整下列 s3a:// 路徑）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
BUCKET_NAME=data-lake
BRONZE_TABLE_PATH=s3a://data-lake/bronze/raw_features/
SILVER_TABLE_PATH=s3a://data-lake/silver/cleaned_features/
SILVER_OCR_TABLE_PATH=s3a://data-lake/silver/ocr_features/
GOLD_WORD_COUNT_PATH=s3a://data-lake/gold/word_frequency/
GOLD_TOPIC_SNAPSHOT_PATH=s3a://data-lake/gold/topic_snapshot/
# 寫入痛點快照後是否強制讀表驗證（預設 true；表極大或除錯可設 false）
# GOLD_TOPIC_SNAPSHOT_VERIFY_AFTER_WRITE=true
# 可留空（預設用容器/環境已安裝 jieba）；僅在 executors 無 jieba 時再指定 zip
# JIEBA_ZIP_PATH=s3a://data-lake/jars/dependencies/jieba.zip
# JIEBA_USERDICT_PATH=s3a://data-lake/jars/dependencies/jieba_userdict.txt
# JIEBA_USERDICT_DATASET_PATTERN=s3a://data-lake/jars/dependencies/jieba_dicts/{dataset_id}.txt
# STOPWORDS_PATH=s3a://data-lake/jars/dependencies/stopwords.txt
# STOPWORDS_DATASET_PATTERN=s3a://data-lake/jars/dependencies/stopwords/{dataset_id}.txt
RAW_IMAGE_PREFIX=raw/images/
RAW_IMAGES_PATH=s3a://data-lake/raw/images/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OCR（Docker 映像已含 chi_tra + eng；Windows 本機可指定執行檔）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OCR_LANG=chi_tra+eng
# TESSERACT_CMD=C:/Program Files/Tesseract-OCR/tesseract.exe

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 上傳：同名物件已存在 — suffix=改檔名加時間戳（預設）；overwrite=覆寫
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# UPLOAD_ON_DUPLICATE=suffix
# MAX_UPLOAD_MB=15

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Flask / 日誌 / 埠（對外對應 WEB_PORT）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
PORT=5000
WEB_PORT=5000
FLASK_DEBUG=false
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
# GET /ready 是否預設包含 Spark 檢查（冷啟動較慢；探針建議仍用 GET /health）
# READY_CHECK_INCLUDE_SPARK=false

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 安全與路徑白名單
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ADMIN_TOKEN=change_me
# ALLOWED_DELTA_PATH_PREFIXES=s3a://data-lake/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MinIO 容器對外埠（僅含 minio 服務的 compose）
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# MINIO_API_PORT=9000
# MINIO_CONSOLE_PORT=9001
